  "label": "The Glarewright Exchange",
  "description": "The Glarewright Exchange operates within a salt-cemented arcade off Brineshade Terminator City’s shuttered corridors, its basalt walls faced with matte panels that suppress terminator glare. Tiered shelving and sealed bins hold optical baffles, reflector foils, and mineral-glass filters standardized to the city’s surveyed approach lines. A recessed counter and calibrating bench dominate the central floor, laid out for precise fitting and inspection under controlled luminance. Vent grilles and dust traps line the thresholds, keeping the mineral haze out of the shop’s enclosed inventory.",
